{"tid":1375654,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［人手置頂728上環見］香港首次旗手小隊上線啦！","createTime":"2019-07-28T06:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T13:02:53.000Z","uid":233174,"like":83,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"163b9925b5c132f2d720be62b9b95eed7184f427","tid":1375654,"uid":233174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"爆左post唔識解1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374922</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n為防散水撚揸住大聲公騎劫前線幾點幾點一齊走<br />\n我地組成左旗手小隊正式喺連登發表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地會有跟實前線一齊共同進退嘅旗手<br />\n會同前線溝通完，得到前線認同，再舉旗俾後排大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n</span><br />\n其實721 727都有旗手出動過<br />\n但應該唔多人知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n728係集合左前兩次終於firm到<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">終於可以喺連登公佈</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍旗 - 慢慢後退 Back Away Slowly</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TikCkkn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTikCkkn.png&h=bbd8cd69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">需要後退時慢慢可以數住1 2 1 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n只係後退唔等於撤離架親<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅旗 - 停 STOP</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdZvFoU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdZvFoU.png&h=948e73fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">後退或者前進到一定時候需要停一停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請提高警覺隨時準備對應任何突發狀況</span></span><br />\n紅色係搶眼啲 但危唔危險就自行判斷啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑旗 - 前方已發生衝突各位小心 Conflict Occurred Be Careful!!</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ux3DPio.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fux3DPio.png&h=e321433e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">防暴正衝擊防線請提升至最高警覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支援或後退請自行決定</span><br />\n狗隻黑旗時人類都會黑旗<br />\n唔好見黑旗就嚇到瀨<br />\n可以用腦思考下係自己人定係狗旗<br />\n<br />\n以上係今日會出嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3款旗</span></strong> total會有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5set</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">500-700m會有一小組旗手 亦會有大聲公配合</span></strong><br />\n重申<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕對唔係大台 只係俾大家知道前線安排</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以上係728旗手小隊安排<br />\n自知係初步一定有好多不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地經過今日一日試驗後會再反省改進<br />\n有咩可以屌 我地會百屌成才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efab6ab2bf8110d82ed15e97fa66e178bdeed32e","tid":1375654,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"49979cd9f72af3c54b91983a15bffc2ce59a0b20","tid":1375654,"uid":233174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:17:32.000Z","msg":"之前個post點樣可以解到1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023585f78e4764639651d8cdc1fdd65099fb3086","tid":1375654,"uid":233174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:18:22.000Z","msg":