thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTikCkkn.png&h=bbd8cd69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">需要後退時慢慢可以數住1 2 1 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n只係後退唔等於撤離架親<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅旗 - 停 STOP</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdZvFoU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdZvFoU.png&h=948e73fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">後退或者前進到一定時候需要停一停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請提高警覺隨時準備對應任何突發狀況</span></span><br />\n紅色係搶眼啲 但危唔危險就自行判斷啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑旗 - 前方已發生衝突各位小心 Conflict Occurred Be Careful!!</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ux3DPio.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fux3DPio.png&h=e321433e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">防暴正衝擊防線請提升至最高警覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支援或後退請自行決定</span><br />\n狗隻黑旗時人類都會黑旗<br />\n唔好見黑旗就嚇到瀨<br />\n可以用腦思考下係自己人定係狗旗<br />\n<br />\n以上係今日會出嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3款旗</span></strong> total會有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5set</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">500-700m會有一小組旗手 亦會有大聲公配合</span></strong><br />\n重申<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕對唔係大台 只係俾大家知道前線安排</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以上係728旗手小隊安排<br />\n自知係初步一定有好多不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地經過今日一日試驗後會再反省改進<br />\n有咩可以屌 我地會百屌成才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T08:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"